7RnGbXlzLwLTw">Thủ nê ngưu - 守泥牛</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-Trung-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%C4%A9/author-vnduJD_TYrIrUDl9fyOqRw">Tuệ Trung thượng sĩ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Thu-nh%E1%BA%ADt-Qu%E1%BB%B3-ph%E1%BB%A7-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-ho%C3%A0i-ph%E1%BB%A5ng-k%C3%BD-Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-gi%C3%A1m-L%C3%BD-t%C3%A2n-kh%C3%A1ch-nh%E1%BA%A5t-b%C3%A1ch-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-1aKtPZzgdx86nyA-olwbPw">Thu nhật Quỳ phủ vịnh hoài phụng ký Trịnh giám, Lý tân khách nhất bách vận - 秋日夔府詠懷奉寄鄭監李賓客一百韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-ho%C3%A0i-c%E1%BB%95-t%C3%ADch-k%E1%BB%B3-5-V%C5%A9-H%E1%BA%A7u-mi%E1%BA%BFu/poem-mafM1mCUnuDfKwkIjFwb1Q">Vịnh hoài cổ tích kỳ 5 - Vũ Hầu miếu - 詠懷古跡其五－武侯廟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Cung-Do%C3%A3n/X%C3%ADch-B%C3%ADch-chu-trung-ca/poem-js6oe3kPuWEg0IcUcHLCeg">Xích Bích chu trung ca - 赤壁舟中歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Cung-Do%C3%A3n/author-8wX_f--qBGvseLM4iD_Z7A">Trần Cung Doãn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-S%C6%B0-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o/X%C3%ADch-B%C3%ADch-%C4%91%E1%BB%93/poem-bT4GIPnEJSxYYBPIGRxl0g">Xích Bích đồ - 赤壁圖</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-S%C6%B0-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o/author-xomLzH62F_NkzLMPyZ81UA">Ngô Sư Đạo</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
